criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age or older;

          -  Subjects suspected to have UPJO.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Renal failure (Creatinine >150);

          -  Allergy to contrast material;

          -  Ureteral stent;

          -  Nephrostomy tube;

          -  Renal pelvis calculi.
